            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the jam is done, transfer it to a bowl and leave to cool slightly</p><p>Tip: The jam will thicken whilst it cools!</p><p>Wash, then separate the <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>and<strong> </strong>pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice the <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p>",
